x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2022">雷丁和利兹</a>音乐节本周回归，围绕潜在秘密布景的猜测已经开始。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/reading-leeds-2023-10-new-acts-you-need-to-see-radar-3481235">雷丁与利兹 2023：今年音乐节上您需要观看的 10 场新表演</a></strong></li></ul><p>2023 年双场地活动将于 8 月 25 日至 27 日在雷丁的里奇菲尔德大道和利兹的布拉汉姆公园举行。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/reading-and-leeds-festival?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=TUeRTURCWxyNT8CXSVXWIUg%3AUkF11-2OiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里购买剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>今年 R&amp;L 的主角将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foals">Foaals</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/imagine-dragons">Imagine Dragons</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2023-joel-dommett-russell-kane-and-fern-brady-lead-alternative-stage-line-up-3471914">该系列产品</a>中还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">Wet Leg</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/inhaler">Inhaler</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steve-lacy">Steve Lacy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/knucks">Knucks 等</a>。</p><p>昨天（8 月 21 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">Soft Play</a> （以前称为 Slaves） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-fka-slaves-share-new-single-punks-dead-and-announce-surprise-reading-leeds-sets-3486125">宣布他们将于周六（8 月 26 日）在雷丁和周日（27 日）在利兹的 Festival Republic Stage 演出</a>。</p><p>现在，有传言称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girl-in-red">红衣女孩</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">孟买自行车俱乐部</a>都可能作为惊喜特邀嘉宾出现。 </p><figure id="attachment_3233791" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3233791" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3233791" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/2022_girlinred_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="红衣女孩现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/2022_girlinred_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/2022_girlinred_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/2022_girlinred_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/2022_girlinred_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/2022_girlinred_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/2022_girlinred_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3233791" class="wp-caption-text">红衣女孩于 2022 年 4 月 23 日在加利福尼亚州印第奥举行的 2022 年科切拉谷音乐艺术节的莫哈韦帐篷中登台表演。图片来源：Matt Winkelmeyer/Getty Images for Coachella</figcaption></figure><p>据<a href="https://www.leeds-live.co.uk/best-in-leeds/gigs-clubs/two-big-name-acts-look-27556777" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《利兹现场》</em></a>报道，当您在其网站上搜索前者（真名玛丽·乌尔文）时， <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/search?q=Girl+In+Red+" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ticketmaster</a>目前会列出雷丁和利兹的日期。</p><p>这位挪威创作歌手计划于周五（8 月 25 日）和周一（8 月 28 日）在伦敦<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/final-names-announced-for-all-points-east-festival-2023-lineup-3481179">All Points East</a>演出，分别支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-stokes-and-yeah-yeah-yeahs-announced-for-londons-all-points-east-2023-buy-tickets-3385076">The Strokes/Yeah Yeahs Yeahs</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-announced-as-latest-headliners-for-all-points-east-2023-3409286">Haim</a> 。 《红衣女孩》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/girl-in-red-reading-festival-2021-review-photos-3033105">最后一次在 R&amp;L 演出是在 2021 年</a>，在撰写本文时，本周六和周日免费。 </p><div class="GRl5yb a8pxAe"><div id="JTPWx" class="FJIcp BhBPtb" role="tablist" data-hveid="CBYQAA"><p>与此同时，孟买自行车俱乐部开玩笑说，他们也可能会出现在现场。在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a>合作的最新单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-and-holly-humberstone-team-up-on-diving-3471153">“Diving”</a>发行后，该乐队引用了 Reading &amp; Leeds 官方 Twitter (X) 帐户的一条推文。</p><p> “如果我们今年能在@OfficialRandL 的舞台上播放这首歌曲就好了<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f914.png" alt="🤔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ，”孟买自行车俱乐部写道。 “我们来想办法吧<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">如果我们今年能在<a href="https://twitter.com/OfficialRandL?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@OfficialRandL 的</a>舞台上表演就好了<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f914.png" alt="🤔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />我们来想办法吧<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/RGHxqQTqzA">https://t.co/RGHxqQTqzA</a></p><p> - 孟买自行车俱乐部 (@BombayBicycle) <a href="https://twitter.com/BombayBicycle/status/1682409488760930304?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 21 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>乐队定于周四（8 月 24 日）在布里斯托尔 Rough Trade 演出，但随后将在本周剩余时间演出。</p><p>亨伯斯通将于周六在雷丁的东主舞台和周日在利兹的主舞台上演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-festival-2023-stage-set-performance-times-schedule-3485334">您可以在此处查看 2023 年雷丁和利兹的完整赛段和比赛时间</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-festival-2023-weather-forecast-3485288">在此处查看两个地点的最新天气预报</a>。</p><p>在其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-steps-up-security-to-weed-out-drug-dealers-3484477">R&amp;L 组织者证实，他们已经加强了安全措施，以“清除”在现场活动的毒贩</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/campfires-bbqs-and-disposable-vapes-banned-from-reading-leeds-2023-3477632">禁止篝火、烧烤和一次性电子烟</a>。</p><p><strong><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/reading">请返回 NME，</a>了解 Reading &amp; Leeds 2023 的最新新闻、评论、采访、照片等。<br /></em></strong></p></div></div><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/two-big-names-look-set-for-secret-sets-at-reading-leeds-2023-3486479">两位大牌明星将在 2023 年雷丁和利兹举行秘密演出的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 和沃伦·埃利斯 (Warren Ellis) 宣布推出新的“Australian Carnage”现场专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-warren-ellis-announce-new-australian-carnage-live-album-preorder-3486525?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nick-cave-warren-埃利斯宣布新澳大利亚大屠杀现场专辑预购Liberty DunworthTue, 22 Aug 2023 10:03:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3486525 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Nick Cave and the Bad Seeds 乐队的 Nick Cave 和 Warren Ellis 于 2022 年 7 月 4 日在意大利维罗纳演出。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们希望他们能捕捉到我们在这些演出中感受到的集体喜悦的十分之一”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-warren-ellis-announce-new-australian-carnage-live-album-preorder-3486525">Nick Cave 和 Warren Ellis 宣布新的“Australian Carnage”现场专辑</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Nick Cave and the Bad Seeds 乐队的 Nick Cave 和 Warren Ellis 于 2022 年 7 月 4 日在意大利维罗纳演出。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nick-Cave-Warren-Ellis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warren-ellis">沃伦·埃利斯 (Warren Ellis)</a>宣布了一张新现场专辑的详细信息，该专辑是根据他们去年在悉尼歌剧院的三场表演创作的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/nick-cave-interview-hope-faith-carnage-new-bad-seeds-grinderman-cancel-culture-coronation-3448005">尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）：“没有任何衡量标准表明美德造就优秀的艺术”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>该专辑名为“Australian Carnage”，收录了两人在澳大利亚城市表演的音频，这是他们 2022 年底在该国进行 16 站巡演的一部分。这次巡演庆祝了 2021 年禁闭专辑《Australian Carnage <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nick-cave-warren-ellis-carnage-review-2887522">》</a>的发行。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nick-cave-warren-ellis-carnage-review-2887522">Carnage&#39;</a>中，Cave 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds">Bad Seeds 的</a>长期成员 Ellis 聚在一起开展了一个新的内省副业项目。</p><p>这张现场专辑将以两种不同的形式发行：包含 18 首曲目的数字版本，将于本周五（8 月 25 日）发行；以及包含 8 首曲目的黑胶唱片版本，将于 12 月 1 日通过 Goliath 上市 -<a href="https://nickcaveandwarrenellis.lnk.to/AusCarnageSOH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订</a>。</p><p>为了庆祝这一消息，凯夫和埃利斯还分享了选自即将发行的专辑的《Balcony Man》的现场版本。在下面找到它。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：Balcony Man - 悉尼歌剧院现场演出" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/67lXj28wxvk4d6HWQClYkh?si=b345542a9b9b4415&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p> “在离开这么久之后，与沃伦一起巡演澳大利亚是近年来的亮点之一，”凯夫在解释这张现场专辑背后的原因时说道。</p><p> “每场演出都令人感动且难忘，从剧院和艺术中心的亲密演出，到悬岩的广阔而令人振奋的夜晚，再到我们在无与伦比的悉尼歌剧院度过的最后三晚。”</p><p>他补充道：“我们很高兴分享这些在悉尼歌剧院录制的录音，并希望它们能捕捉到我们在这些演出中感受到的集体喜悦的十分之一。我们永远不会忘记他们。”</p><p> 12 月 16 日、17 日和 18 日在悉尼标志性歌剧院举行的演出中，Radiohead 的 Colin Greenwood 和常规 Bad Seed Larry Mullins 以及伴唱 Wendi Rose、Janet Ramus 和 T Jae Cole 也加入了这对二人组的演出。</p><p>请查看下面的“澳大利亚大屠杀 - 悉尼歌剧院现场演出”的专辑封面以及两首曲目列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3486536" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3486536" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3486536" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="“澳大利亚大屠杀 - 悉尼歌剧院现场演出”艺术作品" width="2000" height="2005" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000-800x802.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000-1392x1395.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Australian-Carnage-artwork@2000x2000-1068x1071.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3486536" class="wp-caption-text"> “澳大利亚大屠杀——悉尼歌剧院现场演出”艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“澳大利亚大屠杀”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p><strong>数字相册：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.《旋转歌》</strong><br /> <strong>2.“亮马”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“夜袭”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“大屠杀”</strong><br /> <strong>5.《白象》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“幽灵”</strong><br /> <strong>7.《薰衣草田》</strong><br /> <strong>8.《等你》</strong><br /> <strong>9.“我需要你”</strong><br /> <strong>10.《宇宙舞者》</strong><br /> <strong>11.“气喘吁吁”</strong><br /> <strong>12.《上帝之手》</strong><br /> <strong>13.《破碎的土地》</strong><br /> <strong>14.“大帆船”</strong><br /> <strong>15.《利维坦》</strong><br /> <strong>16.《阳台人》</strong><br /> <strong>17.“好莱坞”</strong><br /> <strong>18.《鬼魂说话》</strong></p><p><strong>黑胶唱片：</strong></p><p><strong>第 1 面：</strong><br /> <strong>1.《亮马》</strong><br /> <strong>2.“大屠杀”</strong><br /> <strong>3.《白象》</strong><br /> <strong>4.《利维坦》</strong></p><p><strong>第 2 面：</strong><br /> <strong>1.“幽灵”</strong><br /> <strong>2.《等你》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“气喘吁吁”</strong><br /> <strong>4.《阳台人》</strong></p><p> Cave 和 Ellis 于 2021 年 2 月发行的《Carnage》专辑获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nick-cave-warren-ellis-carnage-review-2887522"><em>NME</em>的五星级评价</a>，Andrew Trendell 形容该专辑标志着乐队达到了“他们力量的顶峰”。</p><p>此外，当二人组于当年晚些时候将现场表演带到英国时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/nick-cave-warren-ellis-london-croydon-fairfield-halls-carnage-tour-live-review-3037709">伦敦的表演为他们赢得了另一项五星级评价</a>，演出组合了《Carnage》、《Ghosteen》和《Skeleton Tree》中的曲目。评论中写道，这将这场演出变成了一场“适度雄心勃勃的新现场奇观”，磨练了一种“亲密”的感觉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3485312" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3485312" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3485312" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nick-cave-Andreas-RentzGetty-Images.jpg" alt="尼克·凯夫" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nick-cave-Andreas-RentzGetty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nick-cave-Andreas-RentzGetty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nick-cave-Andreas-RentzGetty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nick-cave-Andreas-RentzGetty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nick-cave-Andreas-RentzGetty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nick-cave-Andreas-RentzGetty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3485312" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：安德烈亚斯·伦茨/盖蒂图片社。</figcaption></figure><p>在 Nick Cave 的其他新闻中，今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/nick-cave-interview-hope-faith-carnage-new-bad-seeds-grinderman-cancel-culture-coronation-3448005">这位艺术家与<em>NME</em>谈论</a>了对下一张 Bad Seeds 专辑的期待，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-on-the-new-bad-seeds-album-and-the-chances-of-more-from-grinderman-3449133">Grinderman 是否有机会很快推出更多音乐</a>。</p><p> “我们可以制作一张 Grinderman 唱片，因为 Grinderman 本质上是即兴创作。这在音乐上具有挑战性，你真的不知道你会得到什么，但我认为我们不能再制作一张四人摇滚唱片了，”他说。</p><p>在其他地方，就在上个月，他还在自己的<a href="https://www.theredhandfiles.com/do-you-believe-in-the-concept-of-a-soulmate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Red Hand Files 网站</a>上提交了一条条目，告诉粉丝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-is-currently-finishing-the-new-bad-seeds-album-3472170">他目前正在“完成”与 Bad Seeds 的新专辑的制作工作</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-warren-ellis-announce-new-australian-carnage-live-album-preorder-3486525">Nick Cave 和 Warren Ellis 宣布新的“Australian Carnage”现场专辑</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
